{"tid":1875285,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】廣東台推抗疫應援歌 被踢爆抄襲「乃木坂46」hit歌","createTime":"2020-02-11T16:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T17:53:41.000Z","uid":29627,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0bd011090d50c560f9df3344c99dedda59995f4b","tid":1875285,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:34:51.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】廣東台推抗疫應援歌 被踢爆抄襲「乃木坂46」hit歌<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/B9GGterqwx5zIfkru7KIP_f5Wvs=/1920x1080/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/K7RKSZ2Y6GLWY6W5ZJLDANSZ3E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FB9GGterqwx5zIfkru7KIP_f5Wvs%3D%2F1920x1080%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FK7RKSZ2Y6GLWY6W5ZJLDANSZ3E.jpg&h=086d3fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣東電視台珠江頻道的抗疫歌曲，被指抄襲乃木坂46暢銷單曲。<br />\n<br />\n內地又爆抄襲當創作事件。廣東電視台珠江頻道日前推出抗疫歌曲《願望成真》，為武漢肺炎病人、醫護人員加油打氣，不過卻被網友發現旋律似曾相識，疑似抄襲日本女團「乃木坂46」的暢銷單曲《同步巧合》。<br />\n<br />\n《願望成真》是由內地音樂人黃志遠作詞作曲，珠江頻道主持人任永全、「環市東十二妹」劉穎婷等演唱。歌曲發佈後卻被網友發現，疑似抄襲日本女團「乃木坂46」的《同步巧合》。有網友對比2首歌的音軌、旋律，指《願望成真》只是稍微改變節奏和幾個音調，整體旋律和《同步巧合》幾乎一模一樣。<br />\n<br />\n有網民更指，乃木坂46在內地已經有一定的知名度，去年還在上海舉行了演唱會，《願望成真》疑抄襲的又是曾奪得唱片大賞、在紅白獻唱過的歌曲，「自然是炸開了鍋！」<br />\n<br />\n有份參與演唱的歌手劉穎婷，本月7日於微博上道歉：「收到乃木坂46粉絲們的關注和提醒，理解大家的心情。為最大可能尊重作者及版權，現決定刪除有爭議原帖。抱歉給大家帶來困擾。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，《願望成真》作曲人黃志遠卻否認抄襲，更反批質疑的人是對音樂製作不了解，讓大批網友氣炸，留言狠酸「可能你們『願望成真』了，可是我們卻被『同步巧合』了」，「同步巧合啦」。<br />\n<br />\n亦有網民揶揄：「蠢爆了，誰不抄偏偏去抄當紅的被秒抓包」、「簡直一模一樣，甚麼音樂家就是個搬運工吧」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200212/BSNJVJNO2XPAH6MNYFFIUMGKLA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200212%2FBSNJVJNO2XPAH6MNYFFIUMGKLA%2F&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BaHX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=fc4f438c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200212%2FBSNJVJNO2XPAH6MNYFFIUMGKLA%2F&h=65067883\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200212/BSNJVJNO2XPAH6MNYFFIUMGKLA/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5gluqjijzvY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5gluqjijzvY&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BaHX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=cd6cd0d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5gluqjijzvY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f0wbnQw89J0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Df0wbnQw89J0&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BaHX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=846d5288\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f0wbnQw89J0</a>"},{"pid":"3529b8587215900c7d6da7a7f13e5ed2ad3d6108","tid":1875285,"uid":288210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:53:41.000Z","msg":"啲支那人剩係識抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}